Package: ConditionalScoreDecomp
Type: Package
Title: Conditional decomposition of the Brier score into uncertainty, resolution, and reliability components
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-02-03
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Sam", family = "Allen", email = "sam.allen@unibe.ch", role = c("cre", "aut")))
Description: Functions to assess probability forecasts for binary events using 
    the Brier score, and decompose the score into measures of forecast
    uncertainty, resolution, and reliability. This decomposition can also be
    performed conditional on certain events having occurred.
URL: https://github.com/sallen12/ConditionalScoreDecomp
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    gridExtra,
    scales,
    reliabilitydiag
Suggests: 
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
